cast.overview: In 1800s England, a well-meaning but selfish young woman meddles in the love lives of her friends.
cast.title: Emma.

details.biography: Amber Anderson is an English actress, pianist and model. She is best known for her roles as Jane Fairfax in the 2020 film Emma, Ciara Porter in J.K Rowling's crime drama series Strike, Lady Anne in The Riot Club (2014), and She in the Steve McQueen-directed Mr. Burberry (2016). She also starred as Lady Diana Mitford in Peaky Blinders (2022). She is also a pianist and violinist.
details.name: Amber Anderson
